          Graduated from the Bangladesh Youth Leadership Center, a prestigious
          institution fostering leadership and professional development.
        </li>
        <li>
          Completed a comprehensive program emphasizing leadership skills,
          strategic thinking, and effective communication.
        </li>
        <li>
          Engaged in coursework that provided a strong foundation in ethical
          leadership and community impact.
        </li>
      </ul>
    </TimeLineElement> -->
    <TimeLineElement
      title="Bachelor of Science in Computer Science"
      subtitle="International University of Business Agriculture and Technology (IUBAT), Dhaka, Bangladesh"
    >
      <ul class="list-disc ml-5">
        <li>Currently pursuing a BSE in Computer Science at IUBAT.</li>
        <li>Expected graduation in 2025.</li>
      </ul>
    </TimeLineElement>
  </div>

  <div class="mb-5">
    <div class="text-3xl w-full font-bold">Experience</div>
  </div>

  <div class="time-line-container mb-10">
    <TimeLineElement
      title="User Experience Designer"
      subtitle="From 2019 at ReShop · Dhaka, Bangladesh"
    >
      Embarked on my professional journey as a Junior UX Designer at ReShop.
      Contributed to enhancing user interactions and interfaces, gaining
      valuable experience in user-centric design principles. Collaborated within
      a dynamic team environment, laying the foundation for my evolving career
      in software development.
    </TimeLineElement>
    <TimeLineElement
      title="Full Stack Developer"
      subtitle="From 2019 to 2022 at Softenin · Dhaka, Bangladesh"
    >
      As a Full-Stack Developer at Softenin, I contributed to the end-to-end
      development of a mobile application for a startup company that aims to
      revolutionize the healthcare industry by providing an easy-to-use platform
      for patients to access healthcare services online, demonstrating
      proficiency in both frontend and backend technologies.
    </TimeLineElement>
    <TimeLineElement
      title="Chief Technology Officer, KLwebco"
      subtitle={`From 2022 · Huntington, New York, United States`}
    >
      As CTO of KLwebco, I lead the technological vision and strategy,
      overseeing software design, development, and architecture. Steering the
      company through innovation, I drive the implementation of cutting-edge
      solutions to achieve KLwebco's goals.
    </TimeLineElement>
  </div>

  <div class="mb-5">
    <div class="text-3xl w-full font-bold">Key Projects</div>
  </div>

  <div class="time-line-container mb-10">
    {
      recentProjects.map((project) => (
        <TimeLineElement
          title={project.title}
          subtitle={`${project.year} · ${project.technologies.join(", ")}`}
        >
          <p class="text-justify">{project.description}</p>
          <div class="mt-2">
            <a
              href={project.url}
              target="_blank"
              class="text-primary hover:underline"
            >
              View Project →
            </a>
          </div>
        </TimeLineElement>
      ))
    }
  </div>

  <div class="mb-5">
    <div class="text-3xl w-full font-bold">Certifications</div>
  </div>

  <ul class="list-disc mx-6 mb-10 grid gap-2">
